The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, country, pop
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, watermelon, pineapple
3 different pets are kept: dog, frog, hedgehog
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, oliveros, pall-mall
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
 2. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 3. the fan of country is between the oliveros-smoker and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 4. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the frog##1
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the scientist##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | sprite         | iced-tea  | lemonade      |
| Hobby         | writing        | dancing   | filmmaking    |
| Job           | security-guard | scientist | social-worker |
